    <p><b>4. Camping</b></p> 
    <img alt="" class="style10" src="../TourismHUB/Packages/Images/auli4.jpg" />
    <p>Camping is the most popular activity you can enjoy in Auli town. According to visitors, you can get a mesmerizing experience for a lifetime here. In this camp, you can spend a night beside a bonfire while enjoying delicious local foods.

</p>
<p>Moreover, in these camps, you can sleep under the stars enjoying the weather. During these camping, tourists will find themselves very close to mother nature. Some of these camps can also offer you several other activities during camping, such as- drifting the woods, trekking, hiking, etc..</p>